								</svg>
							</div>
							<div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bsn-navy font-display mb-3">
									Profitability
								</h3>
								<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
									Data-driven strategies to maximize profitability and operational efficiency.
								</p>
